rows.label: tlk41100141_01_msg0001
rows.name:
The island I lived on became
uninhabitable because of the
skirmishes between Invidia and Superbia.

rows.label: tlk41100141_01_msg0002
rows.name:
The adults just argued about
which side to join, which one
would be more profitable.

rows.label: tlk41100141_01_msg0003
rows.name:
In the end, everyone on the island
split into pro-Superbia and pro-Invidia
factions and started fighting.

rows.label: tlk41100141_01_msg0005
rows.name:
Vandham says not all of
them are like that...

rows.label: tlk41100141_01_msg0006
rows.name: But I can't bring myself to trust them.
